sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Mgr as Manager / Test
    participant Topic as m2e/verb
    participant Router as CommandRouter
    participant Queue as Event queue
    participant Runtime as EvSimRuntime
    participant FSM as fsm::v2 FSM

    Mgr->>Topic: publish JSON payload
    Topic->>Router: MQTT handler
    Router->>Queue: enqueue Event
    Queue-->>Runtime: wake_fd.notify()
    Runtime->>FSM: on_wake -> feed(ev)
